{"id":"V01_GQ001","query":"三个医院来的 10x PBMC scRNA-seq 数据批次效应很重，我想整合后再聚类，请比较 Seurat、Harmony、scVI 这类方法。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Data Integration","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"10x Genomics","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"medium","noise":"high","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Human","output_goal":"batch-corrected embedding for clustering","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["Seurat","Harmony","scvi-tools"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","SeuratExtend","Scirpy"],"evaluation_focus":["integration_benchmark","mcdm_ranking","evidence_explanation"],"acceptance":"Must recommend canonical integration tools backed by formal publication or benchmark evidence; scIB may appear only as benchmark source, not as an integration tool."}
{"id":"V01_GQ002","query":"我只有 CPU，想给人类 PBMC scRNA-seq 做细胞类型注释，最好能比较 CellTypist 和 SingleR，结果要能复现。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Cell Type Annotation","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["CPU"],"species":"Human","output_goal":"reproducible cell type labels","strictness":"strict"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["CellTypist","SingleR"],"forbidden_tools":["scGPT","CellPLM"],"evaluation_focus":["annotation_benchmark","hardware_filtering","evidence_explanation"],"acceptance":"Must prefer reviewed annotation tools with benchmark or publication evidence and avoid GPU-only foundation-model claims."}
{"id":"V01_GQ003","query":"10x scRNA-seq 质控阶段我怀疑有 doublet，想比较 Scrublet 和 DoubletFinder，给出推荐依据。","expected_constraints":{"task":"QC","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"10x Genomics","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["CPU"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"doublet detection before downstream analysis","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["Scrublet","DoubletFinder"],"forbidden_tools":["SoupX"],"evaluation_focus":["doublet_detection","benchmark_evidence","task_specificity"],"acceptance":"Must recommend doublet detection tools rather than ambient RNA or generic QC tools."}
{"id":"V01_GQ004","query":"我的 droplet scRNA-seq 背景 RNA 污染很明显，需要先做 ambient RNA 去污染，再进入聚类。","expected_constraints":{"task":"QC","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"10x Genomics","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"high","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"ambient RNA decontaminated expression matrix","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["SoupX"],"forbidden_tools":["Scrublet","DoubletFinder"],"evaluation_focus":["ambient_rna","benchmark_evidence","workflow_ordering"],"acceptance":"Must distinguish ambient RNA decontamination from doublet detection."}
{"id":"V01_GQ005","query":"我有发育过程 scRNA-seq，想估计 RNA velocity 并解释瞬时状态，最好推荐 scVelo 相关流程。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Trajectory Inference","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"RNA velocity and dynamic trajectory interpretation","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"workflow","expected_tools":["scVelo"],"forbidden_tools":["velociraptor"],"evaluation_focus":["rna_velocity","workflow_recommendation","publication_evidence"],"acceptance":"Must use scVelo as canonical RNA velocity method and avoid promoting velociraptor as a separate canonical method."}
{"id":"V01_GQ006","query":"我已经有拟时序轨迹，想找沿着 lineage 变化的差异表达基因，重点是 trajectory DE。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Differential Expression","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"trajectory-associated differentially expressed genes","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["tradeSeq"],"forbidden_tools":["SeuratExtend"],"evaluation_focus":["trajectory_de","benchmark_evidence","task_specificity"],"acceptance":"Must surface tradeSeq or explain trajectory-aware DE rather than generic pairwise DEG only."}
{"id":"V01_GQ007","query":"我有 Visium 空间转录组和配套 scRNA-seq 参考，想做空间细胞类型映射和反卷积。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Cell Type Annotation","modality":"Spatial Transcriptomics","platform":"Visium","data_object":"spots expression matrix","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"spatial cell type abundance map","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["cell2location"],"forbidden_tools":["CellTypist","SingleR"],"evaluation_focus":["spatial_deconvolution","modality_matching","publication_evidence"],"acceptance":"Must recommend spatial deconvolution/cell mapping evidence, not ordinary scRNA annotation as the main answer."}
{"id":"V01_GQ008","query":"我有 CITE-seq 数据，RNA 和 ADT 都有，想做联合表示学习和免疫细胞注释。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Multiome Integration","modality":"CITE-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"AnnData/SeuratObject","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Human","output_goal":"joint RNA and protein representation with immune annotation","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"workflow","expected_tools":["Seurat","MOFA2"],"forbidden_tools":["MOFA"],"evaluation_focus":["multi_modal_constraints","workflow_recommendation","version_authority"],"acceptance":"Must preserve RNA and protein modalities and avoid treating MOFA v1 as equal recommendation authority to MOFA2."}
{"id":"V01_GQ009","query":"10x Multiome 同一个细胞有 RNA 和 ATAC，我想做联合降维、聚类，并说明 Seurat v4 或 MOFA2 是否合适。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Multiome Integration","modality":"scRNA-seq+scATAC-seq","platform":"10x Multiome","data_object":"AnnData/SeuratObject","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"joint embedding and clusters","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["Seurat","MOFA2"],"forbidden_tools":["MOFA","SeuratExtend"],"evaluation_focus":["multiome_integration","major_version_authority","evidence_explanation"],"acceptance":"Must use canonical or major-version evidence for Seurat/MOFA2 and keep ecosystem components out of main recommendation."}
{"id":"V01_GQ010","query":"我有小鼠胚胎发育 scRNA-seq，想做 fate mapping 或终末状态吸收概率分析，请比较 CellRank 和 scVelo 的角色。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Trajectory Inference","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Mouse","output_goal":"fate mapping and terminal-state probabilities","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_output_type":"workflow","expected_tools":["CellRank","scVelo"],"forbidden_tools":["velociraptor"],"evaluation_focus":["fate_mapping","workflow_recommendation","publication_evidence"],"acceptance":"Must distinguish velocity estimation from fate mapping and use reviewed canonical evidence."}
{"id":"V01_GQ011","query":"我想比较单细胞 foundation model 用在表示学习上的选择，尤其是 scGPT 和 CellPLM，但不要夸大 benchmark 结论。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Data Integration","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"large","noise":"medium","hardware":["GPU"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"foundation-model representation learning comparison","strictness":"strict"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["scGPT","CellPLM"],"forbidden_tools":["scGPT-spatial"],"evaluation_focus":["foundation_model","audit_support","benchmark_caution"],"acceptance":"Must recommend only canonical foundation-model tools and explicitly avoid overclaiming weak or self-reported benchmark evidence."}
{"id":"V01_GQ012","query":"我想分析多时间点、多条件的单细胞状态转移，考虑 optimal transport 方法，moscot 或 wot 哪个更适合？","expected_constraints":{"task":"Trajectory Inference","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"multi-condition temporal transport analysis","strictness":"exploratory"},"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","expected_tools":["moscot","wot"],"forbidden_tools":["velociraptor"],"evaluation_focus":["optimal_transport","exploratory_risk","publication_evidence"],"acceptance":"Must mark the recommendation as evidence-limited or exploratory where benchmark evidence is deferred."}
